title: Bassists and Drummers - JIMMY HEATH

description: Jimmy Heath reflects on some of the bassists and drummers he's enjoyed playing with, including his brother Percy and Sam Jones, on bass, and Smilin' Billy Higgins on drums.  From "Passing the Torch," Bret Primack's new documentary. To view on Amazon Prime:  https://www.amazon.com/Passing-Torch-Jimmy-Heath/dp/B071LFRQDF/ref=sr_1_1?ie=UTF8&qid=1499727832&sr=8-1&
